{"type":"message","id":"65491741","parentId":"ede12fa4","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:27:57.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to fix the group message format. The issue is the literal \"\\n\" appearing in the message instead of a real line break. I need to look at the feishu_send_group.mjs script to see how to fix this.\n\nThe current message shows: `bug单已提交：「狡兔三窟」技能导致人机对手不结束回合\\n链接：https://...`\n\nThe `\\n` should be a real newline, not a literal backslash-n. The fix should be in the script that sends the group message.\n\nLet me check the script to understand how to fix this properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01HpZHNxf8N5XToFUKGWiwAd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_group.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779247668449,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2486c361-442e-4c45-b39e-451470f917e4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ec2d88b","parentId":"65491741","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:27:58.260Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01HpZHNxf8N5XToFUKGWiwAd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 飞书群消息发送工具\n * 使用 OpenClaw 配置的 appId/appSecret 获取 tenant_access_token 后发送消息\n */\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVp…OGKv';\n\nasync function getTenantAccessToken() {\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Get token failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\n/**\n * 发送飞书群消息（富文本，支持 @ 提及）\n * @param {string} chatId - 群 chat_id，如 oc_xxx\n * @param {string} text - 消息文本（支持 <at user_id=\"xxx\">name</at> 格式）\n */\nexport async function sendGroupMessage(chatId, text) {\n  const token = await getTenantAccessToken();\n\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`,\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({\n      receive_id: chatId,\n      msg_type: 'text',\n      content: JSON.stringify({ text }),\n    }),\n  });\n\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Send message failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.data?.message_id;\n}\n\n// 预设消息模板（避免命令行引号转义问题）\nconst TEMPLATES = {\n  'hotupdate-ok': '热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>',\n  'hotupdate-fail': '❌ 热更流水线失败，请检查日志',\n};\n\n// 直接运行时的入口\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst rawText = process.argv[3] || 'hotupdate-ok';\n// 支持模板名或直接文本\nconst text = TEMPLATES[rawText] ?? rawText;\n\nsendGroupMessage(chatId, text)\n  .then(msgId => {\n    console.log('发送成功！message_id:', msgId);\n  })\n  .catch(e => {\n    console.error('发送失败:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779247678260}}
{"type":"message","id":"e89af737","parentId":"6ec2d88b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:28:04.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题在于群消息里的 `\\n` 没有被转义成真正的换行，而是字面量显示出来了。需要修改脚本，让命令行传入的文本支持 `\\n` 转换为真实换行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01PxKsVFgmweANsitpLFfmnw","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_group.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"// 支持模板名或直接文本\nconst text = TEMPLATES[rawText] ?? rawText;","newText":"// 支持模板名或直接文本，并将字面 \\n 转换为真实换行\nconst text = (TEMPLATES[rawText] ?? rawText).replace(/\\\\n/g, '\\n');"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779247678261,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e26f72cb-e597-4634-8079-3c5b1a3e8b2e"}}
