- UI\n   → https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/view/1131253609001038156\n\n**已发群消息：**\n- ✅ 客户端母单通知 → 发送成功\n- ✅ UI 子需求通知 → 发送成功\n<<<END_UNTRUSTED_CHILD_RESULT>>>\n\nStats: runtime 35s • tokens 7.1k (in 6.2k / out 962) • prompt/cache 13.7k\n\nAction:\nA completed subagent task is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type).\n<<<END_OPENCLAW_INTERNAL_CONTEXT>>>"}],"timestamp":1779281235575,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:e3b61651-4be4-4024-9cff-c4cb82f03b23","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4bc0d47","parentId":"d20aa87c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:47:18.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sub-agent completed successfully. Both stories were created and group messages sent. I need to deliver this to the user in my normal voice.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 搞定～\n\n**① 客户端需求单（母单）**\n优化主界面的设置按钮\n→ https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/view/1131253609001038152\n\n**② UI 子需求（关联到母单）**\n主界面设置按钮优化 - UI\n→ https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/view/1131253609001038156\n\n群里也通知了～处理人都是你，母单的预设子项：客户端+策划+QA，UI单的预设子项：UI+UI验收+策划+QA ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":24554,"output":166,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34704,"cost":{"input":0.00343756,"output":0.00004648,"cacheRead":0.00027955199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037635919999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779281235579,"responseId":"cc48b0a6-0af7-4933-950d-ea49aa3e3b5a"}}
