{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fef0f6938bcb28c747116a1ad2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 21:16 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"ded5e42d","parentId":"302abf77","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:15.220Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"db50df8f","parentId":"ded5e42d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:17.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人要我设置胡新雷的 Git 仓库权限为报告者（Reporter）。这需要用到 GitLab 权限管理 Skill。\n\n先读取 Skill 文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_D2y6RxC6QUje1QZzvsiN7317","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":38828,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38922,"cost":{"input":0.00543592,"output":0.000026320000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00546224}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779282975220,"responseId":"5f5a7617-b3b2-4ecf-9c1b-a1f85c80cc70"}}
{"type":"message","id":"26525177","parentId":"db50df8f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:17.962Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_D2y6RxC6QUje1QZzvsiN7317","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gitlab-permission\ndescription: 管理 git.devcloud.ztgame.com 上的 GitLab 项目成员权限。支持添加/删除/修改成员，查询项目成员列表。  \n  触发词：git权限、加git权限、管理git、项目成员、gitlab权限。  \n  适用：yyzy_proj 组下的项目，叶枝君账号（Maintainer/Owner 权限）。\n---\n\n# GitLab 权限管理\n\n## 前置条件\n\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`（已保存 _gitlab_session）\n- 仅对叶枝君具有 **Maintainer(40)** 或 **Owner(50)** 权限的项目可操作\n\n## 管理的项目组（5 个核心仓库）\n\n当说「给 XX 加项目权限」时，以下 5 个仓库全部加 Developer(30)：\n\n| # | 仓库 | ID | 我的权限 |\n|:-:|------|:--:|:--------:|\n| 1 | yyzy_proj/1v1/config | 5058 | Maintainer ✅ |\n| 2 | yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig | 4710 | Owner ✅ |\n| 3 | yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework | 5048 | Developer ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 4 | yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1 | 5145 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 5 | yyzy_proj/1v1/proto | 5060 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n\n> 注：仓库 3-5 需要主人先给叶枝君提升到 Maintainer 权限才能管理。\n\n## 其他可管理的项目\n\n| 项目 | ID | 权限 |\n|------|:--:|:----:|\n| yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon | 2751 | Owner |\n| didastudio/cdn_251121 | 5638 | Maintainer |\n| yezhijun1/cdn_solo | 5871 | Owner |\n\n## 权限等级\n\n| 等级 | 名称 | 值 |\n|:----:|------|:--:|\n| 10 | Guest | 访客 |\n| 20 | Reporter | 报告者 |\n| 30 | Developer | 开发者 |\n| 40 | Maintainer | 维护者 |\n| 50 | Owner | 拥有者 |\n\n## 已知用户 ID\n\n| 姓名 | 用户名 | ID |\n|------|--------|:--:|\n| 叶枝君 | @yezhijun | 983 |\n| 周以天 | @v-zhouyitian | 1003 |\n| 陈霄豪 | @chenxiaohao | 1134 |\n\n## API 用法\n\n```javascript\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n```\n\n### 查询项目成员\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/all?per_page=100\n```\n\n### 批量添加到 5 个核心仓库（给项目加权限）\n```bash\nnode scripts/git_permission.mjs batch <用户名称> developer\n```\n\n### 添加成员（单一仓库）\n```bash\nPOST /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members\nBody: user_id={user_id}&access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 修改成员权限\n```bash\nPUT /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\nBody: access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 删除成员\n```bash\nDELETE /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\n```\n\n### 搜索用户\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/users?search={用户名}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779282977962}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdbc1af9","parentId":"26525177","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:21.055Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the skill says:\n- 当说「给 XX 加项目权限」时，以下 5 个仓库全部加 Developer(30)\n- 但这次主人说\"设置为报告者\"（Reporter = 20），不是 Developer\n\n胡新雷这个用户不在已知用户 ID 列表中，需要先搜索他的 user_id。\n\n另外，主人没有指定具体项目，所以应该按照 skill 的默认规则，对 5 个核心仓库操作。但这里有两个问题：\n1. 仓库 3-5 叶枝君没有管理权限，不能操作\n2. 权限值是 Reporter(20) 而不是默认的 Developer(30)\n\n所以可以操作的仓库只有：\n- yyzy_proj/1v1/config (5058) - Maintainer ✅\n- yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig (4710) - Owner ✅\n\nLet me first search for 胡新雷's GitLab user ID, then apply the changes.\n\nLet me check the git_permission.mjs script to see what helper functions exist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Git 权限管理。先搜胡新雷的 user ID，然后给可管理的仓库加 Reporter 权限。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TgBxfsju416xABwXz3V12056","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":872,"output":308,"cacheRead":38912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40092,"cost":{"input":0.00012208,"output":0.00008624,"cacheRead":0.0010895359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001297856}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779282977963,"responseId":"6d495941-e3a0-44f8-a6c2-88600d643bd7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68a0b183","parentId":"fdbc1af9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:21.074Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_TgBxfsju416xABwXz3V12056","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * GitLab 权限管理工具\n * \n * 用法:\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs list <project_id>                          # 查看项目成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs add <project_id> <user_name> <level>       # 添加成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs update <project_id> <user_name> <level>    # 修改权限\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs remove <project_id> <user_name>            # 删除成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs search <keyword>                           # 搜索用户\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs projects                                    # 列出可管理的项目\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs batch <user_name> <level>                   # 批量添加到5个核心仓库\n * \n * 权限等级: guest(10) / reporter(20) / developer(30) / maintainer(40) / owner(50)\n */\n\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'gitlab_cookies.json');\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nconst LEVEL_MAP = {\n  guest: 10, '10': 10,\n  reporter: 20, '20': 20,\n  developer: 30, '30': 30,\n  maintainer: 40, '40': 40,\n  owner: 50, '50': 50,\n};\nconst LEVEL_NAMES = { 10: 'Guest', 20: 'Reporter', 30: 'Developer', 40: 'Maintainer', 50: 'Owner' };\n\nfunction getHeaders() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  return { 'Cookie': cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; '), 'Accept': 'application/json', 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' };\n}\n\nasync function searchUser(keyword) {\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/users?search=${encodeURIComponent(keyword)}&per_page=10`, { headers: getHeaders() });\n  const users = await r.json();\n  if (!Array.isArray(users) || users.length === 0) return console.log('未找到用户:', keyword);\n  return users.map(u => ({ id: u.id, name: u.name, username: u.username }));\n}\n\nasync function findUsers(name) {\n  const users = await searchUser(name);\n  if (!users) throw new Error(`找不到用户: ${name}`);\n  if (users.length === 1) return users[0];\n  // 精确匹配\n  const exact = users.find(u => u.name === name || u.username === name.replace('@', ''));\n  if (exact) return exact;\n  console.log(`找到多个用户匹配 \"${name}\"，请指定更精确的名称:`);\n  users.forEach(u => console.log(`  ${u.name} (@${u.username})`));\n  throw new Error('多匹配');\n}\n\nasync function listMembers(projectId) {\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${projectId}/members/all?per_page=100`, { headers: getHeaders() });\n  if (!r.ok) { const t = await r.text(); throw new Error(`API error: ${t.substring(0, 100)}`); }\n  const members = await r.json();\n  console.log(`项目成员 (${members.length} 人):`);\n  members.forEach(m => console.log(`  ${m.name} (@${m.username}) - ${LEVEL_NAMES[m.access_level] || m.access_level}${m.id === 983 ? ' (就是你)' : ''}`));\n}\n\nasync function addMember(projectId, userName, level) {\n  const user = await findUsers(userName);\n  const headers = getHeaders();\n  const body = new URLSearchParams({ user_id: String(user.id), access_level: String(LEVEL_MAP[level]) });\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${projectId}/members`, { method: 'POST', headers, body: body.toString() });\n  const result = await r.json();\n  if (r.ok) console.log(`✅ 已添加 ${user.name} (@${user.username}) 为 ${LEVEL_NAMES[result.access_level]}`);\n  else console.error(`❌ 失败:`, result.message || JSON.stringify(result));\n}\n\nasync function updateMember(projectId, userName, level) {\n  const user = await findUsers(userName);\n  const headers = getHeaders();\n  const body = new URLSearchParams({ access_level: String(LEVEL_MAP[level]) });\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${projectId}/members/${user.id}`, { method: 'PUT', headers, body: body.toString() });\n  const result = await r.json();\n  if (r.ok) console.log(`✅ 已更新 ${user.name} (@${user.username}) 为 ${LEVEL_NAMES[result.access_level]}`);\n  else console.error(`❌ 失败:`, result.message || JSON.stringify(result));\n}\n\nasync function removeMember(projectId, userName) {\n  const user = await findUsers(userName);\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${projectId}/members/${user.id}`, { method: 'DELETE', headers: getHeaders() });\n  if (r.ok || r.status === 204) console.log(`✅ 已移除 ${user.name} (@${user.username})`);\n  else { const t = await r.text(); console.error(`❌ 失败:`, t.substring(0, 200)); }\n}\n\nasync function listProjects() {\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects?membership=true&per_page=100&min_access_level=40`, { headers: getHeaders() });\n  const projects = await r.json();\n  console.log(`可管理的项目 (${projects.length}):`);\n  projects.forEach(p => console.log(`  ${p.path_with_namespace} (id=${p.id}) - 我的权限: ${LEVEL_NAMES[p.permissions?.project_access?.access_level] || '?'}`));\n}\n\n// 5 个核心仓库（给项目加权限时全部添加）\nconst CORE_PROJECTS = [\n  { id: 5058, name: 'yyzy_proj/1v1/config' },\n  { id: 4710, name: 'yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig' },\n  { id: 5048, name: 'yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework' },\n  { id: 5145, name: 'yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1' },\n  { id: 5060, name: 'yyzy_proj/1v1/proto' },\n];\n\nasync function batchAddMember(userName, level) {\n  const user = await findUsers(userName);\n  const levelNum = LEVEL_MAP[level];\n  if (!levelNum) throw new Error(`无效等级: ${level}`);\n  \n  console.log(`添加 ${user.name} (@${user.username}) 为 ${LEVEL_NAMES[levelNum]} 到 ${CORE_PROJECTS.length} 个仓库:\\n`);\n  \n  const headers = getHeaders();\n  let success = 0, fail = 0;\n  for (const proj of CORE_PROJECTS) {\n    const body = new URLSearchParams({ user_id: String(user.id), access_level: String(levelNum) });\n    const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${proj.id}/members`, { method: 'POST', headers, body: body.toString() });\n    const result = await r.json();\n    if (r.ok || r.status === 201) {\n      console.log(`  ✅ ${proj.name} - 已添加`);\n      success++;\n    } else if (r.status === 409) {\n      console.log(`  ⚠️ ${proj.name} - 已是成员`);\n      success++;\n    } else {\n      console.log(`  ❌ ${proj.name} - ${result.message || JSON.stringify(result).substring(0, 80)}`);\n      fail++;\n    }\n  }\n  console.log(`\\n结果: ${success} 成功, ${fail} 失败`);\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cmd = process.argv[2];\n  if (!cmd) {\n    console.log('用法: node scripts/git_permission.mjs <命令> [参数...]');\n    console.log('命令: list, add, update, remove, search, projects, batch');\n    return;\n  }\n\n  try {\n    if (cmd === 'list') await listMembers(process.argv[3]);\n    else if (cmd === 'add') await addMember(process.argv[3], process.argv[4], process.argv[5]);\n    else if (cmd === 'update') await updateMember(process.argv[3], process.argv[4], process.argv[5]);\n    else if (cmd === 'remove') await removeMember(process.argv[3], process.argv[4]);\n    else if (cmd === 'search') {\n      const users = await searchUser(process.argv[3]);\n      if (users) users.forEach(u => console.log(`${u.name} (@${u.username}) id=${u.id}`));\n    }\n    else if (cmd === 'projects') await listProjects();\n    else if (cmd === 'batch') await batchAddMember(process.argv[3], process.argv[4] || 'developer');\n    else console.log('未知命令:', cmd);\n  } catch(e) { console.error('错误:', e.message); }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779282981074}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0312ba2","parentId":"68a0b183","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:24.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script is well structured. I need to:\n\n1. First search for 胡新雷's user ID\n2. Then add him as Reporter(20) to the 5 core projects... wait, but some of those projects Yezhijun doesn't have permission to manage (DidaFramework=5048, battle1v1=5145, proto=5060).\n\nBut the batch command will handle the 409/error cases gracefully - it will only succeed on the ones it can. So let me just use `batch` with level `reporter`.\n\nActually wait - this task is going to take a few seconds for the API calls but it's relatively fast. Let me check if any of these actions exceed the 10s threshold... The batch operation makes 5 API calls sequentially, each with a user search first. It should be reasonably fast though.\n\nLet me just run it directly since it's API calls, not a browser automation. Should be quick.\n\nActually, let me first search for 胡新雷 to find their user ID, then batch add.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先搜一下胡新雷的 GitLab 用户信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Ruck0w4OhDvXciJkO97x3084","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace && node scripts/git_permission.mjs search 胡新雷","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2198,"output":321,"cacheRead":40064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42583,"cost":{"input":0.00030772000000000004,"output":0.00008988,"cacheRead":0.001121792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001519392}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779282981075,"responseId":"af120b80-5b4a-4b9c-b80b-54bfc4d11e78"}}
