{"type":"message","id":"8695da82","parentId":"7aea5bee","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:16:46.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cookie is valid - it returns 200 and shows 叶枝君. So the 401 error from the batch script is something else. Let me check the headers more carefully. The issue might be that the API endpoint `/api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members` has a different behavior when the project doesn't exist or the user doesn't have sufficient permissions.\n\nWait, looking at the script more carefully:\n\n```javascript\nfunction getHeaders() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  return { 'Cookie': cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; '), 'Accept': 'application/json', 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' };\n}\n```\n\nAnd in batchAddMember:\n```javascript\nconst headers = getHeaders();\nconst body = new URLSearchParams({ user_id: String(user.id), access_level: String(levelNum) });\nconst r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${proj.id}/members`, { method: 'POST', headers, body: body.toString() });\n```\n\nThis looks correct. But maybe the issue is that the Content-Type header is wrong for URLSearchParams. When you use `body.toString()`, the content type should be `application/x-www-form-urlencoded`, which it is. Let me try a direct POST to one of the repos to debug.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Cookie 有效。我直接试一下 API 调用，看看具体什么原因报 401。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_h07wBxsN7f50JeqYxQag0663","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => c.name + '=' + c.value).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json', 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' };\n\nconst body = new URLSearchParams({ user_id: '1836', access_level: '20' });\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/5058/members', {\n  method: 'POST', headers, body: body.toString()\n});\nconst text = await r.text();\nconsole.log('Status:', r.status);\nconsole.log('Response:', text.substring(0, 500));\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\test_gitlab_add.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":91,"output":569,"cacheRead":44416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45076,"cost":{"input":0.000012740000000000002,"output":0.00015932,"cacheRead":0.001243648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001415708}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283002016,"responseId":"5a78737d-2ad1-4e96-8d0f-bcb52eb10b27"}}
