{"type":"message","id":"88c2db87","parentId":"2d27a29a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:17:16.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"CSRF token approach works! The 409 \"already a member\" means the user is already a member of those projects. But the user wants to set it as Reporter(20), not whatever it currently is. Since the user is already a member, I need to use UPDATE (PUT) instead of ADD (POST).\n\nThe current level is unknown. Let me check what level 胡新雷 currently has on these projects, then update to Reporter.\n\nActually wait, the batch script earlier showed \"401 Unauthorized\" for all repos, which means it couldn't even check if the user was a member. But now with CSRF token, it shows 409 \"already a member\". So the CSRF token fixed the auth issue.\n\nLet me use PUT (update) to set the level to Reporter.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已是成员，需要改成 Reporter。用 PUT 更新权限。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ghYalH1vQCGWdAoWFfRB8473","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * 更新胡新雷 GitLab 权限为 Reporter\n */\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = 'gitlab_cookies.json';\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nfunction getCookieStr() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  return cookies.map(c => c.name + '=' + c.value).join('; ');\n}\n\nasync function getCsrfToken() {\n  const r = await fetch(GITLAB + '/', { headers: { 'Cookie': getCookieStr() } });\n  const html = await r.text();\n  const match = html.match(/<meta name=\"csrf-token\" content=\"([^\"]+)\"/);\n  if (!match) throw new Error('找不到 CSRF token');\n  return match[1];\n}\n\nconst csrfToken = await getCsrfToken();\nconst cookieStr = getCookieStr();\nconst headers = {\n  'Cookie': cookieStr,\n  'Accept': 'application/json',\n  'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded',\n  'X-CSRF-Token': csrfToken,\n};\n\n// 胡新雷 user_id=1836, Reporter=20\nconst projects = [\n  { id: 5058, name: 'yyzy_proj/1v1/config' },\n  { id: 4710, name: 'yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig' },\n];\n\nfor (const proj of projects) {\n  // 先查当前权限\n  const r1 = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${proj.id}/members/all?user_ids[]=1836`, {\n    headers: { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' }\n  });\n  const members = await r1.json();\n  const current = Array.isArray(members) ? members.find(m => m.id === 1836) : null;\n  const currentLevel = current ? current.access_level : 'N/A';\n  console.log(`${proj.name}: 当前权限 ${currentLevel} (${current ? 'Reporter/Developer/Maintainer/Owner'.split('/')[currentLevel/10-2]||'?' : '未知'})`);\n\n  if (currentLevel === 20) {\n    console.log(`  → 已经是 Reporter，跳过`);\n    continue;\n  }\n\n  // 更新为 Reporter(20)\n  const body = new URLSearchParams({ access_level: '20' });\n  const r2 = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/projects/${proj.id}/members/${1836}`, {\n    method: 'PUT', headers, body: body.toString()\n  });\n  const result = await r2.json();\n  if (r2.ok) {\n    console.log(`  ✅ 已更新为 Reporter`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`  ❌ 更新失败: ${JSON.stringify(result).substring(0, 150)}`);\n  }\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\gitlab_update_reporter.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":140,"output":898,"cacheRead":47488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48526,"cost":{"input":0.000019600000000000002,"output":0.00025144,"cacheRead":0.001329664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016007039999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283028555,"responseId":"a6fcc79c-d288-4c17-b86b-65cc8a8e6804"}}
