{"type":"message","id":"a60c28f2","parentId":"fe24cd2c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:17:22.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both projects updated successfully:\n- yyzy_proj/1v1/config (5058): Maintainer(40) → Reporter(20) ✅\n- yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig (4710): Developer(30) → Reporter(20) ✅\n\nNow I should also update the git_permission.mjs script's batch function to include CSRF token support, and fix the underlying issue. But for now, let me just inform the user.\n\nWait, actually the user said \"胡新雷的git仓库权限设置为报告者\" - they were asking about a specific project perhaps? Let me think... The skill says \"当说「给 XX 加项目权限」时，以下 5 个仓库全部加\". But this time the user said about setting permissions, not adding a new member. And they said \"胡新雷的git仓库权限\", which could mean all repos.\n\nBut the other 3 repos (DidaFramework 5048, battle1v1 5145, proto 5060) - Yezhijun doesn't have Maintainer/Owner access on those, so I can't manage them.\n\nLet me also clean up the temp scripts and inform the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了，两个我权限足够的仓库都改好了：\n\n- **yyzy_proj/1v1/config**：Maintainer(40) → **Reporter(20)** ✅\n- **yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig**：Developer(30) → **Reporter(20)** ✅\n\n另外 3 个仓库（DidaFramework、battle1v1、proto）我没管理权限，改不了。对了，原来的权限比较高（Maintainer/Developer），改 Reporter 后他就会失去写入权限，确认这样没问题？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":82,"output":371,"cacheRead":48640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49093,"cost":{"input":0.00001148,"output":0.00010388,"cacheRead":0.00136192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00147728}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779283038687,"responseId":"38897d6c-2cee-420e-971d-60d6f53fcb9b"}}
